OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering showers will clear to the
OL,7,Fsouth this evening, leading to a dry
OL,8,Fnight with clear spells. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly under the clear skies with a
OL,10,Ffew mist and fog patches forming.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FRather cloudy on Tuesday,
OL,13,Fwith a few bright or sunny spells
OL,14,Fdeveloping. Dry for many, but a few
OL,15,Fshowers possibly developing into the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Feeling cool under the
OL,17,Fcloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
