OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FRemaining cool and rather cloudy on
OL,7,FWednesday and Thursday, with a few
OL,8,Fshowers possible. A little warmer
OL,9,Fagain from Friday, with a mix of sunny
OL,10,Fspells and a few showers.
